{
  "stem": "8916.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I know for a fact that, at one point, there was a lot of pressure on Schindler to start manufacturing and producing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was contemplating purchasing products, similar products, and shipping them as if they were produced in his company.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was common knowledge among the inmates at that point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And going-- getting back to that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When my sister was in-- in Plaszow and we were getting ready to-- to go to Brunnlitz on Schindler's list, my father asked Schindler to put my sister on, and he did that.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my sister Aviva and my brother David and I and my parents all ended up on-- in Schindler's company.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He never asked for anything, only-- only our-- our good-- you know, we-- I-- I-- I like to think that we made an honest person out of Schindler.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, he was claiming that we were all skilled people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, we really were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But that's nonsense.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He-- he did that because he couldn't face letting us be murdered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He-- he did-- he's one person who did not accept the Nazi philosophy, and he was not going to go along with it if he could.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he spent a lot of his money that he made.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He came to Poland-- he didn't come to Poland to-- to save Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He came to Poland to make his fortune, and he did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he-- I'm sure it never occurred to him that he was going to end up doing what he did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It just happened that circumstances were such that he was faced with this choice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And being the kind of person he was, he couldn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He couldn't go along with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he did a-- he did a wonderful thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
